data.description: Situated atop beautiful Rarity Mountain is where you will find this well taken care of 3 bedroom, 2 bath house on 3.5 acres. Washer, dryer, range, above range microwave, and refrigerator all stay. A new dishwasher was installed March of 2023. Walk-in closets in all 3 bedrooms. Privacy fence installed December of 2022. The pool is 4' x 18'. A section of the yard was recently leveled out and ready for a barn, camping area, gravel for parking....the options are limitless! For the off-road enthusiast, there is a trailhead into Rarity/Jellico within 2 miles and Royal Blue within 10 minutes on ATV friendly roads. Tackett Creek and North Cumberland are very close as well. Norris Lake only takes approximately 45 minutes to get to. This is house is a manufactured home that has been set to a permanent foundation. It does meet all guidelines and requirements set forth for a FHA loan.
